text:
*Financial Modeling Preview Pro-Sem*

We are very excited to have Professor Brandon Muirhead come for our Pro-Sem this Friday. He will introduce himself, do a couple demo modeling exercises with us, and share his wisdom. He teaches one of the most popular classes in the program. It is full for next semester with a long wait list. If you’re enrolled or are curious for next year, please come!

It’s back to normal this week, so it will be from 9:30-10:45am in room w208. A light breakfast will be provided.
